,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"大屠殺列車（Holocaust train）是德意志國鐵路經營的國家鐵路系統，納粹德國為了強行驅逐猶太人的目的，利用大屠殺列車運送受害者至德國納粹集中營、勞動營與滅絕營。"},{"pid":"a61a0281685c2085ea5f0df59267073b586e5f3c","tid":1734281,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47444ccddaaa99603fcaf342f31376273e58d5d","tid":1734281,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"外國燒鐵已經示範左"},{"pid":"53e06da4228c807aacc6f71fb7c4aeaaf1ea3364","tid":1734281,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e63662e63e105481595f29158f42622a5e9910b","tid":1734281,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"831用過啦"},{"pid":"8c723a415829aa36ac477c6aa7964f38ed2153e8","tid":1734281,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"爆晒所有站玻璃啦"},{"pid":"286d41409c2a1e433ab264996cc9f043577d769f","tid":1734281,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:28:12.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"379c621c2b05ccd6ced894899bccd9a57c497b31","tid":1734281,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:31:03.000Z","msg":"條路軌點解仲無穿無爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff84322cb734faa73f89ebeb1c0389c870d7d94f","tid":1734281,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac